      <p class="pf-sub">Under the <a href="https://www.hse.gov.uk/gas/landlords/index.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gas Safety (Installation and Use) Regulations 1998</a>, every landlord must hold a valid CP12 for every rental property containing gas appliances. Non-compliance carries serious legal consequences.</p>

      <div class="pf-who-grid" style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <div class="pf-who-item" style="border-left:3px solid #dc2626;">
