          <div><strong>Fines up to £6,000 per property</strong><p>The HSE and Sefton Council both enforce gas safety compliance. A single non-compliant Formby property can result in a fine up to £6,000. Criminal prosecution is possible in serious cases.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pf-who-item" style="border-left:3px solid #dc2626;">
